<h1 class="hero-h">Gym startup budget template.</h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A complete 2026 gym startup budget template — 140 line items across 8 categories. Designed to be copied into your own spreadsheet. Use the typical-range columns as starting points; replace with your actual quotes as you collect them.</p>
<div class="toc">
<h4>In this template</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="#facility">1. Facility (lease + buildout)<span class="toc-count">22 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#equipment">2. Equipment<span class="toc-count">28 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#licensing">3. Licensing, permits, insurance<span class="toc-count">14 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#software">4. Software &amp; technology<span class="toc-count">16 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#staff">5. Pre-launch staff &amp; setup<span class="toc-count">12 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#marketing">6. Marketing &amp; pre-launch<span class="toc-count">18 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#workingcapital">7. Working capital (operating reserve)<span class="toc-count">22 lines</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#contingency">8. Contingency<span class="toc-count">8 lines</span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div></div>

<div style="background:#0A1A0A;border-top:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
