<section><div class="sec-inner">
<div class="copy-instructions">
<p><strong>How to use this template:</strong></p>
<p>1. Select all (Cmd-A / Ctrl-A) → copy → paste into Google Sheets or Excel.</p>
<p>2. The template pastes as structured rows; format columns as currency.</p>
<p>3. Replace the "Typical range" column with your actual quotes as you collect them.</p>
<p>4. Add a "Total" cell at the bottom of each category and a grand total at the bottom of the sheet.</p>
<p>5. <strong>Use the <a href="/gym-startup-cost-calculator">interactive calculator</a></strong> for a quick estimate; use this template to build your actual working budget.</p>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- CATEGORY 1: FACILITY -->
<section id="facility"><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">Category 1 · 22 line items</span>
<h2 class="h2">Facility (lease + buildout)</h2>
<div class="cat-section">
<div class="cat-header"><h3>Facility</h3><div class="cat-total">Typical total: $25K-$750K depending on size, market, buildout level</div></div>
<table class="budget-table">
<thead><tr><th>Line item</th><th>Notes</th><th>Typical range</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Security deposit</td><td class="note-cell">2-3 months rent typical</td><td>$10K-$50K</td></tr>
<tr><td>First month rent</td><td class="note-cell">Pro-rated in some cases</td><td>$3K-$25K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Last month rent</td><td class="note-cell">Often required at signing</td><td>$3K-$25K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lease commission (if broker)</td><td class="note-cell">Usually landlord pays</td><td>$0-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lease legal review</td><td class="note-cell">Highly recommended</td><td>$1K-$4K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Architect / space planner</td><td class="note-cell">Required for permits</td><td>$3K-$25K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Permit fees</td><td class="note-cell">Varies by jurisdiction</td><td>$1K-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>General contractor</td><td class="note-cell">Largest buildout line item</td><td>$15K-$400K</td></tr>
<tr><td>HVAC (gyms have unique needs)</td><td class="note-cell">Often biggest single buildout cost</td><td>$5K-$80K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Plumbing (showers, bathrooms)</td><td class="note-cell">Showers add substantial cost</td><td>$3K-$80K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Electrical</td><td class="note-cell">Gym lighting + outlets + AV</td><td>$5K-$40K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Flooring (rubber, turf, hardwood)</td><td class="note-cell">$3-$8/sq ft typical</td><td>$5K-$60K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Mirrors</td><td class="note-cell">Major aesthetic line item</td><td>$2K-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lighting fixtures</td><td class="note-cell">Beyond electrical install</td><td>$2K-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Sound system</td><td class="note-cell">Quality matters for boutique</td><td>$2K-$20K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Paint &amp; finishes</td><td>—</td><td>$2K-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Storage / back-of-house</td><td>—</td><td>$1K-$8K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Reception desk &amp; furniture</td><td>—</td><td>$1K-$10K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Locker room buildout</td><td class="note-cell">If included</td><td>$5K-$60K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Signage (interior + exterior)</td><td>—</td><td>$2K-$20K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Security system</td><td class="note-cell">Cameras + access control</td><td>$2K-$15K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Contingency on buildout (10-20%)</td><td class="note-cell">Always add this</td><td>varies</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div></section>

